---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Biz haqimizda — Clary">
  <section class="container mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-20">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold">Biz haqimizda</h1>
    <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-muted-foreground">
      Clary — O'zbekiston va MDH mamlakatlarining shifoxona, klinika va diagnostika markazlari uchun zamonaviy SaaS platformasi.
      Maqsadimiz: klinikalar qog'oz va Excel'dan voz kechib, bemor xizmatiga vaqt ajratsin.
    </p>
    <h2 class="mt-10 text-2xl font-bold">Bizning qadriyatlarimiz</h2>
    <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-muted-foreground">
      <li>• Bemor ma'lumotlari — eng muhim</li>
      <li>• Shaffof narxlar</li>
      <li>• Tez javob beruvchi support</li>
      <li>• Dunyo standartlari</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</Base>
